{
  "stem": "7546.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was not in the house, it was in the hallway.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were four tenants on the floor, each one shared one toilet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a radio.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's another heartache that I remember very, very dearly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In 1939, shortly before I left Lodz, I carried the radio-- it was a [INAUDIBLE], a big box.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had to carry that into the German headquarters across the street where we lived and give it up because a Jew was not allowed to have a radio.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, do I ever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do I ever.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The first day of the war, I was assigned-- since I was already 16-years-old, I was assigned to be a gopher.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, the-- they were preparing for war in '39.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The war wasn't done yet, but the Polish government gave out all kind of orders, what to do and what not to do.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "First of all, we had to hide lights from the windows, [INAUDIBLE] from the windows.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was one of my jobs, to run around the buildings, look if there's light coming out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was no war yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I used to go with orders-- I mean, I didn't read the orders.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was getting an envelope to go from this section to this section.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I was a gopher.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Unfortunately or fortunately, the war came to our town, which is not too far from the German border, within four days.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I saw the first German soldier driving in to the heart of the town where we lived on a motorcycle.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was a German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, life-- life ended for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It really ended.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Peace and a peaceful life came to a sudden stop, really pressed on the brakes and it stopped.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
